UNICEF aims to achieve this through Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2016, Girls and boys, including adolescents, are protected by social and legal systems at national and community levels against gender-based violence and other forms of violence, abuse and exploitation as well as separation from their families.
